borough: London Borough of Barking and Dagenham
site_name: New England Industrial Estate, Gascoigne Road
description:
Phased development
comprising the partial demolition and extension of Unit 6 for use within Class
Eg(iii), B2 and/or B8, change of use of Unit 3 from waste processing to use
within Class Eg(iii), B2 and/or B8, extension and subdivision of Unit 1 for use
within Class Eg(iii), B2 and/or B8, alterations to the existing access from
Gascoigne Road and re-routing of internal access road, erection of new building
(2 units to be known as Units 7A & 7B) for use within Class Eg(iii), B2
and/or B8 along with parking, servicing, landscaping and related works.
